Create Tar Archive:
tar -cvf backup.tar project/

Extract Archive:
tar -xvf backup.tar

Compress Archive:
tar -czvf backup.tar.gz project/

Extract Gzip Archive:
tar -xzvf backup.tar.gz

Zip Files:
zip backup.zip file.txt

Unzip Files:
unzip backup.zip

Real-Time Scenario:
Backup application before deployment.
tar -czvf app-backup.tar.gz /opt/app
